{"id": "art-25180", "label": "Art. 25180", "title": "Art. 25180", "slug": "art-25180", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1610466660\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1182\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1610466660\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 251<sup>80</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_899709856\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1181\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_899709856\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Divizarea transfrontalier&#259; care a fost supus&#259;\ncontrolului de legalitate, potrivit prezentei <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:\nnormal'>legi</i>, nu poate fi <span class=SpellE>desfiin&#355;at&#259;</span>\ndup&#259; data la care aceasta produce efecte.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1809930081\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1180\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1809930081\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Prin <span class=SpellE>excep&#355;ie</span> de la\nprevederile art. 132 alin. (3), <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunea</span> în\ndeclararea <span class=SpellE>nulit&#259;&#355;ii</span> hot&#259;rârii\nadun&#259;rii generale a <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span> de aprobare\na diviz&#259;rii transfrontaliere poate fi introdus&#259; în termen de 30 de\nzile de la data public&#259;rii acesteia în Monitorul Oficial al României.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2027031900\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1179\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2027031900\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>În cadrul unei <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span> în anulare, formulate potrivit prevederilor\nart. 132 alin. (2), hot&#259;rârea adun&#259;rii generale a <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span>\nnu poate fi anulat&#259; exclusiv pentru:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_693748026\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1178\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_693748026\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)modul de stabilire a ratei de schimb a <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span>, <span class=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;ilor</span>\nsociale sau altor titluri de valoare reprezentând capitalul social;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1111584098\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1177\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1111584098\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)modul necorespunz&#259;tor de stabilire a <span\nclass=SpellE>pre&#355;ului</span> <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span>, <span\nclass=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;ilor</span> sociale sau altor titluri de valoare\nreprezentând capitalul social pentru <span class=SpellE>situa&#355;ia</span>\nexercit&#259;rii de c&#259;tre <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;i</span> a\ndreptului retragerii din societate;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_227326385\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1176\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_227326385\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)nerespectarea <span class=SpellE>cerin&#355;elor</span>\nprivind informarea <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span> asupra <span\nclass=SpellE>pre&#355;ului</span> <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span>, <span\nclass=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;ilor</span> sociale sau altor titluri de valoare\nreprezentând capitalul social pentru <span class=SpellE>situa&#355;ia</span>\nexercit&#259;rii dreptului retragerii din societate sau asupra ratei de schimb\na <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span>, <span class=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;ilor</span>\nsociale sau altor titluri de valoare reprezentând capitalul social.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1578090995\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1175\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1578090995\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Procedurile de anulare <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nde declarare a <span class=SpellE>nulit&#259;&#355;ii</span> nu pot fi <span\nclass=SpellE>ini&#355;iate</span> dac&#259; <span class=SpellE>situa&#355;ia</span>\na fost rectificat&#259;. Dac&#259; neregularitatea ce poate conduce la\ndeclararea <span class=SpellE>nulit&#259;&#355;ii</span> unei diviz&#259;ri\ntransfrontaliere poate fi remediat&#259;, <span class=SpellE>instan&#355;a</span>\ncompetent&#259; acord&#259; un termen pentru rectificarea acesteia.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2101741843\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1174\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2101741843\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>R&#259;spunderea\npenal&#259; <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span class=SpellE>consecin&#355;ele</span>\nacesteia, în cazul <span class=SpellE>s&#259;vâr&#351;irii</span> unei <span\nclass=SpellE>infrac&#355;iuni</span> de c&#259;tre societatea ce a f&#259;cut\nobiectul diviz&#259;rii transfrontaliere, se vor angaja:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_116265660\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1173\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_116265660\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)în cazul unei diviz&#259;ri complete, în sarcina <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>/<span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span>\nbeneficiare, potrivit <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>legii</i>;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1432958761\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1172\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1432958761\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)în cazul unei diviz&#259;ri <span class=SpellE>par&#355;iale</span>\nsau al unei diviz&#259;ri prin separare, atât în sarcina <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\ncare a f&#259;cut obiectul diviz&#259;rii, cât <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nîn sarcina <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>/<span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span>\nbeneficiare.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;text-align:center'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal'><span style='color:black'>TITLUL <span class=SpellE>VII:Lichidarea</span>\n<span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;text-align:center'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal'><span style='color:black'>CAPITOLUL I:Dispozi&#355;ii generale</span></b></p>"}